summary: This document is a telegraphic message from the Federal Aviation Administration confirming the deregistration of a Sikorsky S-76C aircraft (N162AD) from the U.S. Civil Aircraft Register, effective April 10, 2013. The last registered owner was Greenwich AeroGroup Brazil Leasing Inc.

events.title: Deregistration of Aircraft N162AD
events.description: The FAA confirmed the deregistration of the Sikorsky S-76C aircraft from the U.S. Civil Aircraft Register.

keyFacts: The aircraft N162AD was deregistered effective April 10, 2013.
The last registered owner of the aircraft was Greenwich AeroGroup Brazil Leasing Inc.
There were no unreleased recorded liens against the aircraft.
